HEADWORD: Pinetum
<hw>Pi*ne"tum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a pine
grove.]</ety> <def>A plantation of pine trees; esp., a collection of
living pine trees made for ornamental or scientific purposes.</def>⟦br⟧
